    <h1>Managing stock</h1><div id="preamble">
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>On this page you will learn which stock data plentymarkets provides to you, how and where to get an overview of your stocks as well as how to create a reorder. Your stock data is calculated based on your incoming and outgoing items data records.</p>
</div>
<h3 id="_assigning_user_rights_for_back_end_users" class="discrete">Assigning user rights for back end users</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Users of the type <strong>Back end</strong> can only access limited areas and menus in the plentymarkets back end. Thus, their access to the system is limited. If users of this type should be able to work with stocks, a user of the type <strong>Admin</strong> has to assign the rights listed in <a href="#table-rights-stock">Table 1</a> to those users.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Assigning user rights for back end users:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
